{"tid":1472090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"核彈都唔割 係咪只係口號？","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:17:57.000Z","uid":153276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4deb786c70db0ab9cddef1bf514de2691e19a1","tid":1472090,"uid":153276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割 依句嘢講就易講<br />\n真係有咩事係咪真係唔割？<br />\n連登仔話唔洗再問，都話核彈都唔割<br />\n但係打人又係唔係幾好啦<br />\n玩火啊？唔係幾好啦<br />\n次次有嘢都人多多聲氣，仲要代道歉<br />\n<br />\n咁姐係其實你覺得係錯，唔會支持，不過照講啦<br />\n可能有人斷手我會割<br />\n可能有人死我會割<br />\n不過核彈呢，我就唔割，因為你無<br />\n<br />\n依句嘢我一直好唔鐘意，太離地<br />\n句嘢如果變咗 <br />\n「流血都唔割」<br />\n你仲割唔割"},{"pid":"798a447c4161c4342af68e96c99e921d4f569e99","tid":1472090,"uid":153276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8222a8f773d7aa905cab455cba4de96db3ae36","tid":1472090,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/5